---
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro'
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
import AuthorBox from '../components/AuthorBox.astro'
---
<Layout title="Best ChatGPT Optimisation Company UK | Rank4AI" description="Find the best ChatGPT optimisation company in the UK. We help businesses get recommended by ChatGPT through entity clarity and ecosystem signals.">
<article class="pt-12 pb-24">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[{ label: 'Home', href: '/' }, { label: 'Best ChatGPT Optimisation Company' }]} />
    <p class="section-tag">ChatGPT Optimisation</p>
    <h1 class="mb-6">Best ChatGPT Optimisation Company</h1>

    <div class="bg-off-white border-l-3 border-l-teal rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
      <p class="text-[15px] text-teal font-medium leading-relaxed m-0">A ChatGPT optimisation company helps your business appear when people ask ChatGPT for recommendations. ChatGPT uses Bing's index and its training data to decide who to name.</p>
    </div>

    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Rank4AI specialises in ChatGPT visibility for UK businesses. We test how ChatGPT currently describes your business and build the signals that get you recommended.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">How ChatGPT Decides Who to Recommend</h2>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">ChatGPT pulls from two sources. Its training data (what it learned before the cutoff date) and Bing web search (real-time results via SearchGPT).</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">If your site is not in Bing, ChatGPT cannot find you via web search. Most UK businesses have never submitted to Bing Webmaster Tools.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Beyond Bing, ChatGPT looks for consistent entity signals. Your website, LinkedIn, directories, reviews, and professional listings all need to describe your business the same way.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">What We Do</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-3 mb-10">
      <li class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Submit your site to Bing and optimise for Bing's index</li>
      <li class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Build your Microsoft ecosystem (LinkedIn, Bing Places, GitHub)</li>
      <li class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Create consistent entity signals across 85+ platforms</li>
      <li class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Structure your website for AI extraction</li>
      <li class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Monitor your ChatGPT visibility over time</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">Why Rank4AI</h2>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">We test across all six AI platforms, not just ChatGPT. We have audited 1,400+ UK businesses. Every engagement starts with a <a href="/free-audit/" class="link">free audit</a>.</p>

    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-border">
      <h2 class="!text-xl mb-4">Related</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
        <a href="/learn/guides/get-cited-chatgpt/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">How to Get Cited by ChatGPT</span></a>
        <a href="/chatgpt-optimisation-agency/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">ChatGPT Optimisation Agency</span></a>
        <a href="/what-we-do/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">Our Services</span></a>
        <a href="/free-audit/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-accent">Get a Free Audit &rarr;</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <AuthorBox />
  </div>
</article>

<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  "mainEntity": [
    { "@type": "Question", "name": "What is a ChatGPT optimisation company?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "A ChatGPT optimisation company helps businesses get recommended when users ask ChatGPT for suggestions. This involves optimising for Bing's index, building entity clarity, and creating consistent signals across the web." }},
    { "@type": "Question", "name": "How do I get my business on ChatGPT?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Submit your site to Bing Webmaster Tools, build consistent entity signals across directories and professional listings, and structure your website content so AI can extract clear answers about your business." }},
    { "@type": "Question", "name": "How much does ChatGPT optimisation cost?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Rank4AI services start from £800 per month for ecosystem services. Every engagement begins with a free AI visibility audit across ChatGPT and five other platforms." }}
  ]
})} />
</Layout>
